title: #379: Aloha Oe Vey (@ChinoBrah)
itunes:title: Aloha Oe Vey with Chino LaForge
description: Chino LaForge met me before one of our shows to tell me about the history of the country of Hawaii. I think it ain't even really part of America. Honestly. I know it is, but I don't agree. Chino broke down all the history and then we moved on to what it's like there now. Really interested conversation.
